window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Johannes Cabal is a necromancer - and he's slightly infamous. </p> <p><i>Johannes Cabal and the Blustery Day: And Other Tales of the Necromancer</i> features seven of Cabal's most frightening adventures: </p> <ul> <li>\"Exeunt Demon King\" </li> <li>\"The Ereshkigal Working\" </li> <li>\"Johannes Cabal and the Blustery Day\" </li> <li>\"The House of Gears\" </li> <li>\"The Death of Me\" </li> <li>\"Ouroboros Ouzo\" </li> <li>\"A Long Spoon\" </li> </ul> <p>Also included is an original introduction written and read by the author. </p>"; 
